title: Various Artists - Navigatorz Fresh!! Indie Playlist July 2013
description:
This is a fresh!! new!! Indie Playlist of JULY 2013!! Summer is coming. Time for swimming, enjoying in good book and listening your favourite playlists with coctel in another hand.We are happy that we have so many people which downloading our list from month to month. Many new songs, some of them great, waiting for you to give them chance.If you like them please by original CD and support the artists. 
Anyone who is interested in sending your own stuff (via links to downloads), we would gladly listen to your music and include it in our list or radio show if we find it good, so more people would hear it...This month artwork is from Luubenica. 

P.S. we apologies for slow traffic, from time to time, but we are trying our best to improve. We are traveling a lot and most of the lists we are uploading from the completly amazing parts of the globe.Be patient and you will succedeed!!!

Best regards

Navigatorz team

NAVIGATOR, music team producing beats,grooves and much more...And an awesome DJ team and a soundsystem as well proudly presents:

NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! INDIE PLAYLIST JULY 2013

NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! INDIE PLAYLIST contains the team's choice when it comes to independent music acts,ranging from guitar, electronic,acts to so called "indietronica" and experimental sounds...

Enjoy!


P.S. You can WATCH our suggestion for best video on YOUTUBE.On the chanell of GLE Magazin our video playlist20 FRESH!!NEW!! VIDEOS!! SINGLES every month!!!
